OL,3,GOPINIONCBranding implications from
OL,4,CITV/Sky merger
OL,5,
OL,6,FA deal between ITV and Sky's owner
OL,7,FComcast is reportedly nearing
OL,8,Fcompletion.
OL,10,FThe speculation is that Sky will take
OL,11,Fcontrol of ITV 1, ITV X and what we
OL,12,Fused to call the digital channels like
OL,13,FITV 2.
OL,15,FITV plc would still own its production
OL,16,Farm ITV Studios.
OL,18,FThere is speculation ITV plc will
OL,19,Fassume the ownership of production
OL,20,Fcompanies currently owned by Sky as
OL,21,Fpart of the deal.
OL,23,EPub: 15-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,149,140,200,120,0,100
