OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F148A1781698292
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCBranding implications from
OL,4,CITV/Sky merger
OL,5,
OL,6,FUntil a deal is announced ` and agreed
OL,7,Fby shareholders then passed by the
OL,8,Fcompetition authorities ` it is hard to
OL,9,Fdiscuss what it may mean in practice
OL,10,Ffor the public.
OL,12,FBut it's interesting to discuss what it
OL,13,Fcould potentially mean for branding.
OL,15,FI would be shocked if the channel names
OL,16,Fchange and if Comcast does not gain the
OL,17,Fintellectual rights to the ITV brand
OL,18,Fname.
OL,20,FIf this happens, then ITV plc and ITV
OL,21,FStudios will be on the hunt for a new
OL,22,Fname.
OL,23,EPub: 15-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,149,140,200,120,0,100
