PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F148A1781698292
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCBranding implications from
OL,4,CITV/Sky merger
OL,5,
OL,6,FOne online poster suggested an obvious
OL,7,Fcandidate for the new name ` Granada.
OL,9,FIt is familiar to everyone of a certain
OL,10,Fage and properly acknowledges ITV's
OL,11,Fhistory.
OL,13,FITV plc was a merger of Carlton and
OL,14,FGranada but Granada was the dominant
OL,15,Fpartner.
OL,17,FThe irony is that if Granada plc became
OL,18,FITV plc's new corporate name, the last
OL,19,Fremnants of Granada on-screen branding
OL,20,Fin the north west of England would have
OL,21,Fto go. Sky would not have the rights to
OL,22,Fthe name.
OL,23,EPub: 15-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,149,140,200,120,0,100
