OL,3,GOPINIONCBranding implications from
OL,4,CITV/Sky merger
OL,5,
OL,6,FITV News North West would no doubt
OL,7,Fbecome a reality.
OL,9,FWhen a deal is struck, there will be a
OL,10,Flot to debate.
OL,12,FNo doubt some will analyse whether the
OL,13,Fnew company is too dominant. Will Sky
OL,14,Fhave to sell or close some channels in
OL,15,Freturn for picking up ITV 1?
OL,17,FOfcom should double down on enforcing
OL,18,Fpublic service obligations.
OL,20,FThese are by far the two issues which
OL,21,Fmatter most.
OL,23,EPub: 15-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
